# Changelog

All notable changes to **Zano-OriginIP** will be documented in this file.

This project follows the principles of
[Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/)
and adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

---

## [2.1.0] â€“ Major Feature Upgrade

### Added

#### ğŸŒ IPv6 Intelligence Support
- Full IPv6 (AAAA record) resolution alongside IPv4
- Detection of Cloudflare IPv6 ranges (7 official ranges)
- Separate Cloudflare status indicators for IPv4 and IPv6 results

#### ğŸ” Advanced Multi-IP Discovery
- DNS resolution now returns **all associated IPs**, not just the first hit
- Each IP is individually evaluated against Cloudflare ranges
- Output structure:
  - `IPv4: [ip1, ip2, ip3]`
  - `IPv6: [ip1, ip2]`
- CSV exports use semicolon-separated values for multiple IPs

#### ğŸ“Š Real-Time Progress Tracking
- Live progress bar during subdomain enumeration using `tqdm`
- Displays:
  - Elapsed time
  - Estimated time remaining
  - Total scanned domains
  - Cloudflare-protected count
- Automatically disabled in quiet mode (`-q`)

#### â˜ï¸ Dynamic Cloudflare IP Intelligence
- Automatic fetching of Cloudflare IP ranges from official endpoints:
  - `https://www.cloudflare.com/ips-v4`
  - `https://www.cloudflare.com/ips-v6`
- Smart fallback to embedded ranges if API is unreachable
- Runtime logging indicates data source (API vs fallback)

#### ğŸ“ Multi-Format Reporting
- Supported output formats:
  - JSON (`-f json`)
  - YAML (`-f yaml`) â€“ custom serializer (no external dependency)
  - CSV (`-f csv`)
  - Enhanced human-readable terminal output
- Structured reports with clear sections:
  - Origin IPs
  - Cloudflare-protected targets
  - Unresolved domains
  - Errors

#### ğŸ“š Multi-Wordlist Support
- Load multiple wordlists via repeated `-w` flags
- Automatic merging and deduplication
- Individual logging for each loaded wordlist

#### ğŸ”Š Verbosity & Output Control
- Verbose mode (`-v, --verbose`) shows all scan results
- Quiet mode (`-q, --quiet`) outputs only confirmed origin IPs
- Structured logging with verbosity levels

#### ğŸ§  Smart Root Domain Check
- Automatic resolution of the root domain before subdomain enumeration

#### ğŸ§¾ Scan Summary Report
End-of-scan statistics include:
- Total domains tested
- Non-Cloudflare (origin) IP count
- Cloudflare-protected domains count
- Unresolved domains
- Error count

#### ğŸ§¹ Wordlist Parsing Enhancements
- Supports inline comments (`#`)
- Automatically ignores empty lines

#### ğŸ§© Data Models & Typing
- `ResolveResult` dataclass with list-based IP storage
- Separate tracking for:
  - IPv4 / IPv6
  - Cloudflare vs non-Cloudflare IPs
- Computed properties for clean origin IP extraction
- `ScanReport` dataclass with serialization support
- Modular architecture:
  - `CloudflareIPRanges`
  - `ReportWriter`
  - `ZanoOriginIP` (core scanner)
  - `Colors`, `OutputFormat`

